overview.en: EFFORCE is a blockchain-based energy saving trading platform. The platform brings together those who want to improve the energy efficiency of their buildings or industrial processes with a pool of Investors interested in being repaid in tokens representing the energy savings achieved thanks to efficiency improvement projects.
overview.zh: EFFORCE 是基于区块链技术的节能量交易平台。这个平台将希望提高其建筑物或工业设施的能源效率的企业，以及希望通过以代币形式获得能效改造项目所产出的节能量的买家汇集到一起。
